    • fetchAllDoctors

      org.springframework.data.domain.Page<Doctor> fetchAllDoctors(int pageSize, int pageNo)
      Get List of all Doctors with pagination. page Size will be given from end user and it should be more than 0.
      Parameters:
      pageSize - Integer @acceptedValue >0 How many records should placed in a page.
      pageNo - Integer Which page you want to view
      Returns:
      Page
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if pagesize is less than or equal to 0.

      Page
